          <msContents>
            <summary>Manual for use by a priest outlining the methods and rules (laws) related to a sacred diagram intended to honor the nine planets (navagraha) and reflect positively on the person for whom the diagram is being commissioned. Includes two syllabary charts at the end of the manuscript (f. 2v).</summary>
            <textLang>In Sanskrit</textLang>
            <msItem>
              <title>Navagrahayantravidhi</title>
